data.description: Under Construction. Situated on A corner and cul-de-sac homesite, the Highgate 4/2/2 new construction home is meant for entertaining with its prime indoor/outdoor living set up. From its expansive gathering room to the extended covered lanai, this home has room for family and friends to spread out. Designer finishes throughout the home have been hand selected by our professional design team. You are welcomed home by 8’ exterior/interior doors and formal foyer. Enjoy cooking with family and friends in your brand-new kitchen with upgraded 42“kitchen cabinets with roll out trays, soft closing, upgraded SS Whirlpool appliances, and polished chrome cabinet hardware. Stylish 3mc quartz counter tops throughout, backsplash, professional series Shaw laminate flooring in Silo Pine in main living areas, upgraded carpet with 8lb pad in bedrooms.
